wn, knocking out roamers and then the FF house and the TT's. THEN SW corner, the over the South scare tower, then moving over to the samhains, and gorgons (keep in mind Draco roams around in the area east / NE of portal) and then you start moving up the east wall. If you ask a puller to pull gorgons after break in, they will just laugh at you!!! Learn the sequence of events, it will repeat itself next raid! and you will know when your stupid mobs will come!<br><br>#10 Do NOT ATTEMPT CR on your OWN after a failed raid!!!!!. Unless GOD loves you that day, you will just add a nice shiny corpse to the already nice and peachy graveyard.<br>Wait till another crew does it and clears the portal. ( I have lost 46 on my first raid and had to borrow gear from others in order to regain enough xp to GET BACK in there!)<br><br>#11 Do Not go AFK for 30 minutes, two hours, or whatnot because you are dead and you are bored. CR's take time, and the FD corpse puller does not have time to wait for you to waddle back to your keyboard to consent him while he is FD'd with 3 scarelings and a toad standing over him because getting another damn hotpocket out of the microwave was more important that /consenting him. <br><br>Kaane DaSmasher<br> United Independent<br><br>Still applies, after all these years... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/upoppensteelfist.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poppen Steelfist</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 195<br> <font color=#E9D756>(2/18/02 10:35:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3058.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> and!</span><hr size=1> And Don't forget #12<br><br>#12 If at any time you discover a person named Airaman on your fear raid have everyone camp out immediatel