&quot;<br><br>All the while I'm going through the 8th level hell in Feerrott getting tells from everyone's friend's friend asking if I have room for a level 46 necro or asking about loot, etc.  After all groups were in, the camp was trained by the last group arriving.  Every did pretty well there.  All adds were mezzed, and everyone was on a single target.  Out of no where, another group of mobs came and I died attempting to mez them.  When I pop back in from my rez I see Hirosan dragging a body with 3 fiends behind him directly to the camp with 10 people still waiting out rez effects.  Back at my bind point for the second time I asked someone to TL him out.  After my 3rd death he was still there.  UGH.<br><br>This was my first and last pick-up raid.  I'm going back to invitation only. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=59589"><img src="http://hcof.faydwer.com/images/signatures/xargylex.jpg" border="0"><br><center>My profile</center></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uarikel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arikel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 2362<br> <font color=#E9D756>(2/18/02 4:42:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3058.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: and!</span><hr size=1> With everyone and his mom playing a 50+ character and the insanely good gear that's practically there for the taking these days, it blows me away that someone _could_ screw a Fear raid up this badly.  This dude must be a real work of fucking art. <p>Erevan MacQuaide, cleric of Nimue <BR>Ahry Riordan, retired hero of Percival <BR>Arikel Callistrae - retiredmonk of the Erollisi Marr server <BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left>